            "answer_text": "Personally, as someone who has battled depression all my life, I wouldn\u2019t. The condition still has a social stigma attached. You would run the risk that someone reading your essay would consider you a risk for future mental problems. Yes, that\u2019s not accurate or fair, but it\u2019s the way a lot of people view depression. I wouldn t chance it, If you want to focus on your struggles, talk about the life circumstances that triggered the depression and how you were able to rise above them. ",
